ATLANTEAN SLAVE: Escaped survivor of Splugorth captivity

A True Atlantean who escaped Splugorth captivity. Psychically scarred
but resourceful, with hard-won insider knowledge of Splugorth forces
and slave markets. Atlantean Slaves are survivors who have seen the
worst the megaverse offers and kept going.

Slaves know Splugorthian language and are trained in escape artistry,
streetwise tactics, and survival. They carry magical tattoos and a
modest PPE pool. Skill picks come from Physical, Rogue, and Technical
categories.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Race restriction: Atlantean only.
  Attribute requirements: None.
  PPE: Starting pool (ppe_base + ME bonus) grows each level.
  Equipment: Salvaged clothing, one weapon of choice, a concealed
    blade, and detailed knowledge of Splugorth slave markets.

